---
---
<div class="qa-explainer-card">
  <div class="qa-explainer-header">
    <div class="header-icon-wrapper">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="header-svg"><path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="qa-badge">Gating split (ADR 0002 amendment)</span>
      <h3>What the suites verify</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="qa-intro">
    A lane's release verdict is <strong>good</strong> only when build, signature verification, and the gating QA suites all pass. Gating suites prove the image-based, atomic platform contract. Informational suites are tracked, linked, and trended, but they do not block a release.
  </p>

  <div class="suites-grid">
    <div class="suite-card suite-card--gate">
      <div class="suite-card__header">
        <span class="suite-badge badge--smoke">smoke</span>
        <span class="role-pill role-pill--gate">GATE</span>
      </div>
      <h6>GNOME Shell & Apps</h6>
      <p>Desktop startup, system extensions, top-bar menus, and primary app wrappers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="suite-card suite-card--gate">
      <div class="suite-card__header">
        <span class="suite-badge badge--system">system</span>
        <span class="role-pill role-pill--gate">GATE</span>
      </div>
      <h6>Atomic OS Contract</h6>
      <p>bootc status, read-only /usr, staged upgrades, composefs, rollback behavior.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="suite-card suite-card--gate">
      <div class="suite-card__header">
        <span class="suite-badge badge--flatcar">flatcar</span>
        <span class="role-pill role-pill--gate">GATE</span>
      </div>
      <h6>Flatcar VM</h6>
      <p>Flatcar node lifecycle and systemd/container contracts, gating only for the flatcar lane.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="suite-card suite-card--info">
      <div class="suite-card__header">
        <span class="suite-badge badge--common">common</span>
        <span class="role-pill role-pill--info">INFO</span>
      </div>
      <h6>Sandbox & Portals</h6>
      <p>Flatpak portals, polkit overrides, and user-space isolation boundaries.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="suite-card suite-card--info">
      <div class="suite-card__header">
        <span class="suite-badge badge--developer">developer</span>
        <span class="role-pill role-pill--info">INFO</span>
      </div>
      <h6>Dev Toolchains</h6>
      <p>Homebrew paths, rootless Podman, and developer CLI configuration.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="suite-card suite-card--info">
      <div class="suite-card__header">
        <span class="suite-badge badge--software">software</span>
        <span class="role-pill role-pill--info">INFO</span>
      </div>
      <h6>Bazaar Flatpaks</h6>
      <p>Desktop software hubs, Flatpak CLI actions, and app metadata caching.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .qa-explainer-card {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.35) 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .qa-explainer-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .header-icon-wrapper {
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    color: #38bdf8;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .qa-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #38bdf8;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }
  .qa-explainer-header h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #f8fafc;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .qa-intro {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    max-width: 850px;
  }
  .qa-intro strong {
    color: #38bdf8;
  }
  .qa-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(255px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .qa-grid-item {
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .item-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .step-num {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #38bdf8;
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: monospace;
  }
  .qa-grid-item h5 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }
  .qa-grid-item p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }
  .suites-heading {
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem 0;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #94a3b8;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .suites-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .suite-card {
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.85rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
  }
  .suite-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.25);
  }
  .suite-card__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .suite-card h6 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }
  .suite-badge {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.05rem 0.3rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: monospace;
  }
  .badge--smoke { background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1); color: #38bdf8; border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15); }
  .badge--common { background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1); color: #c084fc; border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.15); }
  .badge--developer { background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.1); color: #f472b6; border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15); }
  .badge--software { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1); color: #4ade80; border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15); }
  .badge--system { background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1); color: #fb923c; border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15); }
  .badge--flatcar { background: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.1); color: #fb7185; border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.15); }

  .role-pill {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 0.08rem 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-left: auto;
  }
  .role-pill--gate { background: rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.12); color: #fb7185; border: 1px solid rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.2); }
  .role-pill--info { background: rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.12); color: #7dd3fc; border: 1px solid rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.2); }

  .suite-card h6 {
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0.35rem 0;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }
  .suite-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #64748b;
  }
  .suite-card--gate { border-left: 2px solid rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.35); }
  .suite-card--info { border-left: 2px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.35); }
</style>
